twitter toy
Display data on a twitter user name entered into a form field  
twitter api exercise

installation:
you will need rvm installed

step 1. bundle install

if you get this coffeescript error...
Could not find coffee-script-source-1.1.3 in any of the sources

do the following...
bundle update --source coffee-script-source

after that then

step 2. bundle exec rake db:create

step 3. bundle exec rake db:migrate

step 4. rails s
